+    Parameters
+    ----------
+        f0_values ; array[float]
+            Value of f0 for each particle.

+
+        alpha : float

+    bn2 = empty(pn[1] + 1, dtype=float)
+    bn3 = empty(pn[2] + 1, dtype=float)
+
+    #$ omp parallel private (ip, eta1, eta2, eta3, f0, filling)
